parameters: \nc<>The match is over. How about surrendering quietly?
\nc<>Shut up! Not yet, I haven't lost yet...!!
\nc<>Huh, it's dangerous! Villain might do something, meow!

\nc<>Are you saying that I'm enough even without the support of
the citizens? Ahh?!

\nc<>Villains don't surrender. They might not even have the
concept of it.
\nc<>Originally, they are beings from another world.

\nc<>Sometimes, I felt a sense of discomfort... But judging from
that reaction, it seems like I hit the mark.

\nc<>Well... yeah, you're right. I was originally human. But
what does that matter?
\nc<>Didn't I just say it earlier? Surrender yourself.

\nc<>I would be happy if you could also tell me about the
mastermind who made you do this, but I won't force you to
that extent.

\nc<>If you resist any further, you'll only suffer later. For
your own sake as well--
\nc<>Shut up, shut up, shut up, shut up, shut up...!!

\nc<>If I resist, I'll suffer later? So are you saying that if I
atone for my sins, I can become happy or something, huh?!

\nc<>You're blabbering about it being for my sake, even though
you don't know anything.
\nc<>Can't you say the same thing even after seeing this?!

\nc<>Until a few months ago, I was an unknown streamer. The
gravel scattered everywhere was practically the same.

\nc<>In the aspect of being buried and dying among ordinary
things.

\nc<>However, everything changed after obtaining this physical
ability and muscles!

\nc<>The power of the villain showed me the future! It gave me
the power to live!
\nc<>You want me to let go of this power?

\nc<>Are you telling me to go back into the darkness where I
can't see even an inch ahead?!
\nc<>It's, it's not that kind of meaning...!

\nc<>Don't spout logical arguments when you don't know
anything!

\nc<>There's no need to worry about that! By the way, what they
say doesn't matter either.
\nc<>There's no way the villain's words make any sense, meow!
\nc<>(But that's no different from a villain, ...right?)

\nc<>(It's okay. There's still the next one. Next time, let's
settle it properly.)

\nc<>The number of good listeners increased by 7,000, and the
number of bad listeners increased by 3,000.
